      "use_type": "principal_use",
      "use_name": "Except where driveway or walkway access is required, a 10 ft. (3 m) wide strip of soft landscaping shall be provided abutting the street line, excluding the street line of a 100-series highway. Soft landscaping shall include: i. salt-tolerant groundcover plants; ii. one ornamental shrub for every 100 sq. ft. (9.29 sq. m.) of required landscaped area; and iii. at least one tree with a minimum base caliper of 50 millimetres for every 50 linear ft. (15 linear m) of lot frontage",
